net.sf.extjwnl.dictionary.file

Interface DictionaryFile

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Owned
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DictionaryDiskFile, ObjectDictionaryFile, RandomAccessDictionaryFile
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDictionaryFile, AbstractPrincetonDictionaryFile, AbstractPrincetonObjectDictionaryFile, AbstractPrincetonRandomAccessDictionaryFile, PrincetonObjectDictionaryFile, PrincetonRandomAccessDictionaryFile, PrincetonResourceDictionaryFile, PrincetonResourceObjectDictionaryFile

    public interface DictionaryFile
extends Owned
    Represents a single dictionary file. The "file" can represent something not necessary on the disk: stream, resource.
    Author:
    John Didion (jdidion@didion.net), Aliaksandr Autayeu
